{"tid":1070183,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple Watch check心率其實有幾準？","createTime":"2019-03-20T12:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T06:44:53.000Z","uid":45241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e2b0e6cf96159d96b2f2f5cda7192bd639b65e","tid":1070183,"uid":45241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"最近買左隻apple watch series 3 <br />\n但小心貪玩個心率<br />\n每日都計住個分鐘心跳率<br />\n宜家平日朝早6點起身 11點訓教<br />\n曾經試過一分鐘跳182<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdPEmEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdPEmEF.png&h=19c41e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到呢個數字真係嚇左一跳<br />\n平時返工都會戴黎查下心跳<br />\n但又唔會話做好體力劇烈嘅工作<br />\n想問下有用開apple watch 既巴絲打<br />\n呢d數據參考可唔可信？<br />\n同埋係咪都會唔準？"},{"pid":"09125ca71b473fa812811b56ed46bab43ed1bc8a","tid":1070183,"uid":85219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"我平時心跳係55 bpm <br />\n行個樓梯就變左13x bpm<br />\n雖然feel到自己個心係跳快左<br />\n但會唔會行條30秒行完嘅樓梯就double個心跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd160e9d2ad98b37424ad48dc33ce377b6e35ccc","tid":1070183,"uid":45241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09125ca71b473fa812811b56ed46bab43ed1bc8a","tid":1070183,"uid":85219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"我平時心跳係55 bpm <br />\n行個樓梯就變左13x bpm<br />\n雖然feel到自己個心係跳快左<br />\n但會唔會行條30秒行完嘅樓梯就double個心跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:29:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得有咁既可能"},{"pid":"c5eb5a6e78c6b1de10561f58db739ba37e8607b9","tid":1070183,"uid":74009,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"試過196 ，都係apple watch<br />\n嚇到去睇心臟科，做晒抽血、超聲波 同 24hrs心電圖都話冇野"},{"pid":"5dbd48905e980fd311a50a3f0e9a37a4319d17df","tid":1070183,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:44:53.000Z","msg":"好準"}]}